5.theory:
# Looping (Perulangan)

Perulangan digunakan untuk mengeksekusi blok kode berulang kali.

## 1. for loop
```javascript
// Mencetak angka 1-5
for (let i = 1; i <= 5; i++) {
  console.log(i);
}
// Output: 1, 2, 3, 4, 5
```

## 2. while loop
```javascript
let i = 1;
while (i <= 5) {
  console.log(i);
  i++;
}
// Output: 1, 2, 3, 4, 5
```

## 3. do...while loop
```javascript
let i = 1;
do {
  console.log(i);
  i++;
} while (i <= 5);
// Output: 1, 2, 3, 4, 5
```

## 4. Loop dengan Array
```javascript
let fruits = ["apple", "banana", "orange"];

// for loop
for (let i = 0; i < fruits.length; i++) {
  console.log(fruits[i]);
}

// for...of loop (modern)
for (let fruit of fruits) {
  console.log(fruit);
}
```

## 5. break dan continue
```javascript
// break: menghentikan loop
for (let i = 1; i <= 10; i++) {
  if (i === 5) break;
  console.log(i);
}
// Output: 1, 2, 3, 4

// continue: skip iterasi saat ini
for (let i = 1; i <= 5; i++) {
  if (i === 3) continue;
  console.log(i);
}
// Output: 1, 2, 4, 5
```

## Contoh Praktis:
```javascript
// Menghitung jumlah 1-5
let total = 0;
for (let i = 1; i <= 5; i++) {
  total += i;
}
console.log(total); // 15
```

