# Async/Await - Pemrograman Async Modern

Async/await membuat kode asynchronous lebih mudah dibaca dan ditulis, seperti kode synchronous.

## 1. Basic Async/Await
```javascript
// Fungsi async selalu mengembalikan Promise
async function fetchData() {
  return "Data loaded!";
}

// Menggunakan await untuk menunggu Promise
async function processData() {
  const data = await fetchData();
  console.log(data); // "Data loaded!"
}

processData();
```

## 2. Error Handling dengan Try/Catch
```javascript
async function fetchWithValidation() {
  try {
    const response = await fetch("https://api.example.com/data");
    if (!response.ok) {
      throw new Error(`HTTP error! status: ${response.status}`);
    }
    const data = await response.json();
    return data;
  } catch (error) {
    console.error("Fetch failed:", error.message);
    return null;
  }
}
```

## 3. Sequential vs Parallel Execution
```javascript
// Sequential execution (satu per satu)
async function sequentialRequests() {
  const user = await fetchUser(1);      // Tunggu selesai
  const posts = await fetchPosts(1);    // Baru jalan setelah user selesai
  const comments = await fetchComments(1); // Baru jalan setelah posts selesai
  return { user, posts, comments };
}

// Parallel execution (bersamaan)
async function parallelRequests() {
  const [user, posts, comments] = await Promise.all([
    fetchUser(1),
    fetchPosts(1), 
    fetchComments(1)
  ]);
  return { user, posts, comments };
}
```

## 4. Async Iteration
```javascript
// For-await-of loop untuk async iterables
async function processMultipleUsers(userIds) {
  const results = [];

  for (let id of userIds) {
    try {
      const user = await fetchUser(id);
      results.push(user);
    } catch (error) {
      console.error(`Failed to fetch user ${id}:`, error);
    }
  }

  return results;
}
```

## Contoh Praktis:
