# Object-Oriented Programming dengan Classes

ES6 Classes menyediakan sintaks yang lebih bersih untuk OOP dalam JavaScript.

## 1. Class Basics
```javascript
class Person {
  constructor(name, age) {
    this.name = name;
    this.age = age;
  }

  // Instance method
  greet() {
    return `Hello, my name is ${this.name}`;
  }

  // Getter
  get isAdult() {
    return this.age >= 18;
  }

  // Setter
  set updateAge(newAge) {
    if (newAge > 0) {
      this.age = newAge;
    }
  }
}

// Menggunakan class
const john = new Person("John", 25);
console.log(john.greet()); // "Hello, my name is John"
console.log(john.isAdult); // true
john.updateAge = 26;
```

## 2. Inheritance dengan extends
```javascript
class Student extends Person {
  constructor(name, age, studentId, major) {
    super(name, age); // Panggil constructor parent
    this.studentId = studentId;
    this.major = major;
    this.grades = [];
  }

  // Override method
  greet() {
    return `${super.greet()} and I study ${this.major}`;
  }

  // Method tambahan
  addGrade(grade) {
    this.grades.push(grade);
  }

  get averageGrade() {
    if (this.grades.length === 0) return 0;
    return this.grades.reduce((sum, grade) => sum + grade, 0) / this.grades.length;
  }
}

const alice = new Student("Alice", 20, "S123", "Computer Science");
console.log(alice.greet()); // "Hello, my name is Alice and I study Computer Science"
alice.addGrade(85);
alice.addGrade(92);
console.log(alice.averageGrade); // 88.5
```

## 3. Static Methods dan Properties
```javascript
class MathUtils {
  // Static property
  static PI = 3.14159;

  // Static method
  static calculateCircleArea(radius) {
    return this.PI * radius * radius;
  }

  static max(...numbers) {
    return Math.max(...numbers);
  }
}

// Menggunakan static members tanpa instance
console.log(MathUtils.PI); // 3.14159
console.log(MathUtils.calculateCircleArea(5)); // 78.53975
console.log(MathUtils.max(1, 5, 3, 9, 2)); // 9
```

## 4. Private Fields dan Methods (ES2022)
```javascript
class BankAccount {
  // Private fields (diawali dengan #)
  #balance = 0;
  #accountNumber;

  constructor(accountNumber, initialBalance = 0) {
    this.#accountNumber = accountNumber;
    this.#balance = initialBalance;
  }

  // Public methods
  deposit(amount) {
    if (amount > 0) {
      this.#balance += amount;
      this.#logTransaction('DEPOSIT', amount);
    }
  }

  withdraw(amount) {
    if (amount > 0 && amount <= this.#balance) {
      this.#balance -= amount;
      this.#logTransaction('WITHDRAW', amount);
      return amount;
    }
    return 0;
  }

  getBalance() {
    return this.#balance;
  }

  // Private method
  #logTransaction(type, amount) {
    console.log(`[${this.#accountNumber}] ${type}: $${amount}`);
  }
}

const account = new BankAccount("ACC123", 1000);
account.deposit(500); // [ACC123] DEPOSIT: $500
account.withdraw(200); // [ACC123] WITHDRAW: $200
console.log(account.getBalance()); // 1300
// account.#balance = 5000; // Error: Private field
```

