# DOM Manipulation Dasar

Document Object Model (DOM) adalah representasi HTML document sebagai tree structure yang bisa dimanipulasi dengan JavaScript.

## 1. Selecting Elements
```javascript
// Single element selection
const header = document.getElementById('header');
const firstButton = document.querySelector('.btn');
const mainContainer = document.querySelector('#main .container');

// Multiple elements selection
const allButtons = document.getElementsByClassName('btn');
const allParagraphs = document.getElementsByTagName('p');
const allCards = document.querySelectorAll('.card');
```

## 2. Modifying Element Content
```javascript
// Mengubah text content
const title = document.getElementById('title');
title.textContent = 'New Title';

// Mengubah HTML content
const content = document.getElementById('content');
content.innerHTML = '<strong>Bold text</strong> and normal text';

// Mengubah attributes
const image = document.querySelector('img');
image.setAttribute('src', 'new-image.jpg');
image.alt = 'Description of image';

// Mengubah styles
const box = document.getElementById('box');
box.style.backgroundColor = 'blue';
box.style.padding = '20px';
```

## 3. Creating dan Inserting Elements
```javascript
// Membuat element baru
const newDiv = document.createElement('div');
newDiv.className = 'alert alert-success';
newDiv.textContent = 'Operation successful!';

// Menambahkan ke DOM
// append - tambah di akhir
const container = document.getElementById('container');
container.append(newDiv);

// prepend - tambah di awal
container.prepend(newDiv);

// insertBefore - tambah sebelum element tertentu
const referenceElement = document.getElementById('reference');
container.insertBefore(newDiv, referenceElement);
```

## 4. Removing dan Replacing Elements
```javascript
// Menghapus element
const elementToRemove = document.getElementById('remove-me');
elementToRemove.remove();

// Menghapus dari parent
const parent = document.getElementById('parent');
const child = document.getElementById('child');
parent.removeChild(child);

// Mengganti element
const oldElement = document.getElementById('old');
const newElement = document.createElement('div');
newElement.textContent = 'New Content';
oldElement.replaceWith(newElement);
```

## Contoh Praktis:
```javascript
class TodoList {
  constructor(containerId) {
    this.container = document.getElementById(containerId);
    this.tasks = [];
    this.render();
  }

  addTask(text) {
    this.tasks.push({
      id: Date.now(),
      text: text,
      completed: false
    });
    this.render();
  }

  removeTask(taskId) {
    this.tasks = this.tasks.filter(task => task.id !== taskId);
    this.render();
  }

  toggleTask(taskId) {
    const task = this.tasks.find(task => task.id === taskId);
    if (task) {
      task.completed = !task.completed;
      this.render();
    }
  }

  render() {
    // Clear container
    this.container.innerHTML = '';

    // Create task elements
    this.tasks.forEach(task => {
      const taskElement = document.createElement('div');
      taskElement.className = `task ${task.completed ? 'completed' : ''}`;
      taskElement.innerHTML = `
        <input type="checkbox" ${task.completed ? 'checked' : ''} 
               onchange="todoList.toggleTask(${task.id})">
        <span>${task.text}</span>
        <button onclick="todoList.removeTask(${task.id})">Delete</button>
      `;

      this.container.append(taskElement);
    });
  }
}

